52:42.521 --> 52:44.221
Sahaja Yoga is ’a-Kriya’ yoga.

52:44.396 --> 52:46.999
‘Kriya’ means when you do something is ‘Kriya Yoga'

52:47.200 --> 52:50.280
and “A-Kriya’ yoga is Sahaja Yoga.

52:50.480 --> 52:51.781
I don’t do anything.

52:51.948 --> 52:54.370
